    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The payloads used in Remote ATtestation procedureS (RATS) may require an associated media type for their conveyance, for example, when the payloads are used in RESTful APIs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This memo defines media types to be used for Entity Attestation Tokens (EATs).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
